data.description: Welcome to Harbor Lake Subdivision! This beautiful home boasts cul-de-sac living as well as backing up to a wildflower garden greenspace, no neighbors behind you, only nature. You will immediately notice the professional landscaping that surrounds the home as you walk up to the front door and all of the natural light that beams through the large windows. Open floor concept with an airy atmosphere, high ceilings and fireplace help create the ultimate living experience. Stained wooden cabinets, and stainless-steel appliances. Laundry on the main level along with an oversized primary bedroom and bathroom. Oversized room with vaulted ceilings, jacuzzi tub and walk-in closets. Access to a cocktail deck off of the primary bedroom that connects to a newer deck overlooking the flat, fully fenced backyard with privacy and wildlife beauty. Full level finished walk-out basement with new carpet installed as well as a 4th true bedroom and full bathroom. Cement patio for all the fall firepits and Chiefs parties. Minutes from Smithville Lake, walking distance to neighborhood lake, hiking trail and pool. Inground sprinkler system. Highly rated Smithville Schools with great access to highways and all the shopping and eating at Smithville Square. Seller is offering $5,000 in Seller Paids of the Buyers Choice.
